Eastern magic obelisk
To make the manhunt in Death Canyon less dangerous to the Khadaganian soldiers, a number of magic obelisks have been placed at different points in the canyon. All sorts of useful spells are cast on anyone who uses them.
#subobj  1
Find the Eastern Obelisk
This magic Obelisk is located near the eastern wall of the Canyon.
#subobj  2
Use the Obelisk
It never occurred to the people who put the magic Obelisks in place that they can be used, not only by the soldiers, but by the victims as well
